---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";

---
<MainLayout
  title="Ai integration services"
  description="Our Laravel agency website offers access to the largest software tools pool in the world created by developers for developers."
>

<div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8 max-w-screen-xl">
  <!-- Introductory Paragraph -->
  <p class="mb-8 text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
    Already have a brilliant idea brewing in your mind, or maybe a project that's hitting roadblocks? Whether you're building the next unicorn SaaS, upgrading an old dusty legacy system, or just wanna optimise your current Laravel stack, we're your ride or die, fam.
  </p>

  <!-- Services Heading -->
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Our Laravel Services</h2>

  <!-- Services Grid -->
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-8">
    <!-- Service Card: Full Custom Laravel Builds -->
    <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
      <div class="flex items-center mb-2">
        <span class="text-2xl mr-2">🔧</span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Full Custom Laravel Builds</h3>
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        Whether it's MVPs or Enterprise-grade portals, we deliver production-ready apps with layered architecture, modular design, and TDD practices. Никакой монолитной каши. Только чистый, расширяемый код.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Service Card: API Integrations -->
    <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
      <div class="flex items-center mb-2">
        <span class="text-2xl mr-2">⚙️</span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">API Integrations</h3>
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        Connect your Laravel backend with third-party services like Stripe, PayPal, Twilio, Firebase, AWS, and beyond. Need custom webhooks, OAuth2 integrations, or event-driven microservices? It's our playground. 😎
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Service Card: Performance Optimization -->
    <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
      <div class="flex items-center mb-2">
        <span class="text-2xl mr-2">🚀</span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Performance Optimization</h3>
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        Who wants a slow website? No one. Мы оптимизируем SQL запросы, настраиваем Redis, Horizon, и строим асинхронные очереди для мгновенной обработки данных.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Service Card: Security Hardening -->
    <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
      <div class="flex items-center mb-2">
        <span class="text-2xl mr-2">🛡️</span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Security Hardening</h3>
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        Laravel security is 🔥 out of the box, but layered security? Even better. 从CSRF保护到API加密，我们让你的应用坚不可摧。
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Service Card: Strategic Consulting -->
    <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
      <div class="flex items-center mb-2">
        <span class="text-2xl mr-2">🎯</span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Strategic Consulting</h3>
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        Tech debt, bad architecture, slow releases? If your Laravel app’s growth is stuck, we provide detailed roadmaps, hands-on code reviews, and CTO-level guidance to future-proof your platform. 由经验丰富的开发人员直接提供支持。
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Service Card: Multi-Tenant SaaS -->
    <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
      <div class="flex items-center mb-2">
        <span class="text-2xl mr-2">🌐</span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Multi-Tenant SaaS</h3>
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        Building a platform that hosts multiple businesses under one roof? Multi-tenancy is tricky af if done wrong. Мы используем проверенные паттерны и современные библиотеки для изоляции данных и масштабируемости.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Service Card: DevOps Automation -->
    <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
      <div class="flex items-center mb-2">
        <span class="text-2xl mr-2">🛠️</span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">DevOps Automation</h3>
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        Build pipelines, deploy zero-downtime updates, auto-scale your services. Manual FTP uploads are dead, fam. CICD (Continuous Integration/Continuous Deployment) or bust. 💥
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Service Card: AI and Laravel -->
    <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
      <div class="flex items-center mb-2">
        <span class="text-2xl mr-2">🧠</span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">AI and Laravel</h3>
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        Machine Learning models, LLM APIs, intelligent agents? Bring the AI sauce to your Laravel app without making a mess. 我们可以帮助您整合OpenAI, Ollama, Langchain, 和更多。
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Highlighted Section -->
  <blockquote class="bg-gray-100 p-6 rounded-lg mb-8">
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
      <strong>And the best bit?</strong> Everything is built around <strong>SOLID</strong>, <strong>KISS</strong>, and <strong>DRY</strong> principles, meaning you’re getting a future-proof, easy-to-maintain codebase that your next dev team will actually thank you for. No spaghetti, no headaches.
    </p>
  </blockquote>

  <!-- Concluding Paragraph -->
  <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
    <strong>Let's be real: Laravel is evolving crazy fast</strong> — and so are user expectations. 
    Old-school PHP apps? 💤 Dead. 
    Static HTML? Cute but nah. 
    Modern apps need fast APIs, slick UX, real-time updates, and auto-scaling infra. 
    И если вы выберете нас, то получите больше, чем просто кодеров — получите партнеров по росту. 🚀
  </p>
</div>
</MainLayout>
